thread.title: Mechelle

author: Mechelle
title: Mechelle
text: I happened across PriorTax online when I was looking for an easy way to file my 2015 taxes, which I hadn't done yet in January of 2017. PriorTax walked me through the process quickly and easily. I've used other online tax return sites and PriorTax was by far the easiest and cheapest. As a result I used PriorTax for my 2016 tax return and plan to continue using them in the future.
